<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v6" title="Q19_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En una expresión que describe un cambio de velocidad aparece el factor
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>.
      ¿Cuál de las siguientes es una forma equivalente simplificada de ese factor?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al multiplicar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Esta opción es positiva, por lo que no es equivalente al factor dado.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Se multiplica primero <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y resulta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces el factor completo queda <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, que coincide exactamente con esta alternativa.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El factor dado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> y se simplifica como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Además, esta opción vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, que no coincide con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En el factor original la raíz es <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, no <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>. Esta opción equivale a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> porque <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> es <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. El factor dado vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que no son equivalentes.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la multiplicación</strong></p>
            <p>El factor es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Aquí se multiplica <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> por <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar los coeficientes numéricos</strong></p>
            <p>Se multiplican los números fuera de la raíz:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Mantener el factor radical</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> ya está simplificado, el resultado completo es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La única opción que coincide exactamente con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> es la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La forma equivalente simplificada del factor dado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>